#Simplified Inverse Frequency Weights Matrix: [151.563,1.013,160.263]
#Log Scaled Ln - Inverse Frequency Weights Matrix: [5.028,0.700,5.083]
#Log Scaled Log10 - Inverse Frequency Weights Matrix: [2.092,1.665,2.092]




